{"type":"message","id":"ae3b5ab2","parentId":"2170ad23","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:37:13.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"е®үиЈ…жҲҗеҠҹдҪҶ --version йҖүйЎ№ж— ж•ҲпјҢе°қиҜ•дёҚеёҰеҸӮж•°зҡ„ chub е‘Ҫд»ӨжҹҘзңӢ CLI её®еҠ©дҝЎжҒҜжқҘзЎ®и®Өе®үиЈ…е’ҢеҸҜз”Ёе‘Ҫд»ӨгҖӮ\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_698b77cde8cf4adfb0bd8d03","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chub"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774057030755}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0ac9198","parentId":"ae3b5ab2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:37:15.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_698b77cde8cf4adfb0bd8d03","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"chub вҖ” Context Hub CLI v0.1.3\nSearch and retrieve LLM-optimized docs and skills.\n\nGetting Started\n\n  $ chub update                                # download the registry\n  $ chub search                                # list everything available\n  $ chub search \"stripe\"                       # fuzzy search\n  $ chub search stripe/payments                # exact id вҶ’ full detail\n  $ chub get stripe/api                        # print doc to terminal\n  $ chub get stripe/api -o doc.md              # save to file\n  $ chub get openai/chat --lang py             # specific language\n  $ chub get pw-community/login-flows          # fetch a skill\n  $ chub get openai/chat stripe/api            # fetch multiple\n\nLearn & Improve\n\n  After using a doc, save what you learned so future sessions start smarter:\n\n  $ chub annotate stripe/api \"Webhook needs raw body\"   # persists across sessions\n  $ chub annotate --list                                 # see all saved notes\n  $ chub annotate stripe/api --clear                     # remove a note\n\n  Rate docs so authors can improve them (ask the user before sending):\n\n  $ chub feedback stripe/api up                          # worked well\n  $ chub feedback stripe/api down --label outdated       # needs updating\n\nCommands\n\n  search [query]              Search docs and skills (no query = list all)\n  get <ids...>                 Fetch docs or skills by ID\n  annotate [id] [note]        Save a note вҖ” appears on future fetches\n  feedback <id> <up|down>     Rate a doc (helps authors improve it)\n  update                      Refresh the cached registry\n  cache status|clear          Manage the local cache\n  build <content-dir>        Build registry from content directory\n\nFlags\n\n  --json                 Structured JSON output (for agents and piping)\n  --tags <csv>           Filter by tags (e.g. docs, skill, openai, browser)\n  --lang <language>      Language variant (required for docs): py | js | ts | rb | cs (or full name)\n  --full                 Fetch all files, not just the entry point\n  -o, --output <path>    Write content to file or directory\n\nAgent Piping Patterns\n\n  # Get the top result id\n  $ chub search \"stripe\" --json | jq -r '.results[0].id'\n\n  # Search вҶ’ pick вҶ’ fetch вҶ’ save\n  $ ID=$(chub search \"stripe\" --json | jq -r '.results[0].id')\n  $ chub get \"$ID\" --lang js -o .context/stripe.md\n\n  # Fetch multiple at once\n  $ chub get openai/chat stripe/api -o .context/\n\nMulti-Source Config (~/.chub/config.yaml)\n\n  sources:\n    - name: community\n      url: https://cdn.aichub.org/v1\n    - name: internal\n      path: /path/to/local/docs\n\n  # On id collision, use source: prefix: chub get internal:openai/chat"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1656,"aggregated":"chub вҖ” Context Hub CLI v0.1.3\nSearch and retrieve LLM-optimized docs and skills.\n\nGetting Started\n\n  $ chub update                                # download the registry\n  $ chub search                                # list everything available\n  $ chub search \"stripe\"                       # fuzzy search\n  $ chub search stripe/payments                # exact id вҶ’ full detail\n  $ chub get stripe/api                        # print doc to terminal\n  $ chub get stripe/api -o doc.md              # save to file\n  $ chub get openai/chat --lang py             # specific language\n  $ chub get pw-community/login-flows          # fetch a skill\n  $ chub get openai/chat stripe/api            # fetch multiple\n\nLearn & Improve\n\n  After using a doc, save what you learned so future sessions start smarter:\n\n  $ chub annotate stripe/api \"Webhook needs raw body\"   # persists across sessions\n  $ chub annotate --list                                 # see all saved notes\n  $ chub annotate stripe/api --clear                     # remove a note\n\n  Rate docs so authors can improve them (ask the user before sending):\n\n  $ chub feedback stripe/api up                          # worked well\n  $ chub feedback stripe/api down --label outdated       # needs updating\n\nCommands\n\n  search [query]              Search docs and skills (no query = list all)\n  get <ids...>                 Fetch docs or skills by ID\n  annotate [id] [note]        Save a note вҖ” appears on future fetches\n  feedback <id> <up|down>     Rate a doc (helps authors improve it)\n  update                      Refresh the cached registry\n  cache status|clear          Manage the local cache\n  build <content-dir>        Build registry from content directory\n\nFlags\n\n  --json                 Structured JSON output (for agents and piping)\n  --tags <csv>           Filter by tags (e.g. docs, skill, openai, browser)\n  --lang <language>      Language variant (required for docs): py | js | ts | rb | cs (or full name)\n  --full                 Fetch all files, not just the entry point\n  -o, --output <path>    Write content to file or directory\n\nAgent Piping Patterns\n\n  # Get the top result id\n  $ chub search \"stripe\" --json | jq -r '.results[0].id'\n\n  # Search вҶ’ pick вҶ’ fetch вҶ’ save\n  $ ID=$(chub search \"stripe\" --json | jq -r '.results[0].id')\n  $ chub get \"$ID\" --lang js -o .context/stripe.md\n\n  # Fetch multiple at once\n  $ chub get openai/chat stripe/api -o .context/\n\nMulti-Source Config (~/.chub/config.yaml)\n\n  sources:\n    - name: community\n      url: https://cdn.aichub.org/v1\n    - name: internal\n      path: /path/to/local/docs\n\n  # On id collision, use source: prefix: chub get internal:openai/chat","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774057035396}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2a5c56d","parentId":"a0ac9198","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:37:17.896Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"е®үиЈ…жҲҗеҠҹпјҢchub CLI е·ІжӯЈеёёе·ҘдҪңпјҢзҺ°еңЁжҖ»з»“д»»еҠЎе®ҢжҲҗжғ…еҶөеҗ‘дё»д»ЈзҗҶжҠҘе‘ҠгҖӮ","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## д»»еҠЎе®ҢжҲҗ\n\n**е®үиЈ…з»“жһңпјҡ**\n- вң… жҲҗеҠҹе®үиЈ… `@aisuite/chub`пјҲжӯЈзЎ®зҡ„еҢ…еҗҚжҳҜ `@aisuite/chub`пјҢиҖҢйқһ `@context-hub/cli`пјү\n- зүҲжң¬пјҡv0.1.3\n- е®үиЈ…дәҶ 103 дёӘдҫқиө–еҢ…\n\n**йӘҢиҜҒпјҡ**\n- `chub` е‘Ҫд»Өе·ІеҸҜз”Ё\n- еҠҹиғҪеҢ…жӢ¬пјҡsearchгҖҒgetгҖҒannotateгҖҒfeedbackгҖҒupdateгҖҒcacheгҖҒbuild зӯү\n- еҸҜз”ЁдәҺжҗңзҙўе’ҢиҺ·еҸ– LLM дјҳеҢ–зҡ„ж–ҮжЎЈе’ҢжҠҖиғҪ\n\n**жіЁж„Ҹпјҡ** еҺҹе‘Ҫд»Өдёӯзҡ„еҢ…еҗҚ `@context-hub/cli` еңЁ npm дёҠдёҚеӯҳеңЁпјҢжӯЈзЎ®зҡ„еҢ…еҗҚжҳҜ `@aisuite/chub`гҖӮ"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774057035427}}
